            "title": "日股半日升56點　39000點得而復失",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股39000點水平得而復失，仍未企穩。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數早段最多升近360點，高見39190點，半日收報38888點，升56點，升幅0.15%。</p>\n</div>",
